-------------------------------------
Running this code:

`go run . --help` in this directory to see up-to-date help.

Use flags to indicate what needs to be done to tast test files ("actions")
and how to select which tests are modified ("filters").

e.g.
go run . --localOnly --removeContacts="foo@google.com, bar@google.com" --dryRun

-------------------------------------
Using files as input:
e.g.
go run . --setHwAgnostic --testNames "`cat path/to/file`"

-------------------------------------
Editing this code:
Use `go test ./...` in this directory to execute tests.
